author: David Fischer
title: The adidas Originals EQT Support ADV Returns Entirely Murdered-Out
text:
Visit the original post to see all 3 images from this gallery. 
The adidas Originals EQT Support ADV returns for Spring 2017 not only with a Primeknit upper, but it also almost entirely blacked-out. Except for a contrasting hit on the mid-sole in white and the heel tab, the sneaker comes completely murdered-out in its latest rendition. The Primeknit upper is merged with suede and contrasting synthetic materials across the upper, while keeping the overall appearance very clean. You can pick up the sneaker now from Feature .
